{"tid":1136372,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"為讓山齊士離隊，曼聯願承擔其一部分的薪水，但不願意賣給BIG6","createTime":"2019-05-03T03:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T04:43:58.000Z","uid":30768,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9a54487d9bafe3fda55a22bae1e62689bf347ed8","tid":1136372,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:21:39.000Z","msg":"報道稱，目前山齊士未來的決定權在蘇斯克查手中，不過對於讓智利人離隊，曼聯持開放的態度。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯高層清楚，山齊士50萬英鎊的周薪再加上獎勵對球隊來說是一個很大的障礙，所以為了讓山齊士轉會，曼聯願意支付他一半的薪水，但是他們不願意將山齊士出售給英超big6中的球隊。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯清楚，為一名不在球隊中的球員支付1300萬英鎊的薪水是很困難的決定，但是他們認為騰出每週25萬英鎊的薪金空間對於簽下新球員來說是有利的。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯認為處理山齊士最好的方式是讓他今夏租借離隊，這樣他們可以在2020-21賽季前再和智利人談永久轉會的事情，如果他能在其他球隊找回狀態那是最好的。"},{"pid":"6b5cef96d0f9f3b89ffc2d0270d07a97f8fa373f","tid":1136372,"uid":16061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:25:13.000Z","msg":"到底佢份糧係咪真係50萬磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9400c75a5dfc2575391c1d160d4a66d9abbb05f9","tid":1136372,"uid":58512,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:25:17.000Z","msg":"根本無人接 不願意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d050efff1c32f4221702259dbe9bc9ce2ff8932","tid":1136372,"uid":3194,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:26:01.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過根本冇big 6想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65302e5561abd55c4c608f12100771b56d7c3e2","tid":1136372,"uid":20473,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:27:20.000Z","msg":"25萬周薪都冇人接貨啦傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9958f3c3d38d65742a83272182028546ac691eb5","tid":1136372,"uid":20473,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:27:55.000Z","msg":"真係得中超會收<img src=\"/assets